msgctxt "QL_Gerudo_Ch_Helmet_Desc"
msgid ""
"The Thunder Helm has been passed down as\n"
"a prized treasure of the Gerudo since Urbosa's\n"
"time. It doesn't seem like they'll just give it to\n"
"you, but if you're able to <1.se_co>solve all <2.re_co>the town's\n"
"problems, they'll at least lend it to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Gerudo_Ch_Helmet_Finish"
msgid ""
"You solved the problems of everyone in town!\n"
"\n"
"Riju gave you the Gerudo's symbol of\n"
"friendship, and you got the Thunder Helm!"
msgstr ""

